data.description: Great 3 bedroom 2 bath home in sought after DD2 school district. Laminate floors throughout the living areas with beautiful carpet in bedrooms for those chilly mornings. Upgraded kitchen with granite counter tops overlooking the eat-in-kitchen and family room with wood burning fireplace. A nice bright sun room is off the kitchen and opens to a large fenced backyard.
